Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:08.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周前  從第一次出現受害者時起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:18.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續虛空爆炸事件的爆炸威力以及範圍正在不斷擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:18.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:27.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發現時間和地點的關聯性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:32.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對遺留物品進行的取樣分析中也沒有找到線索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了防止出現下一個受害者  必須與警備員相互協助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:38.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進一步強化各種的警備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並全力以赴解決此次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:28.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚也一直調查到深夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛空爆炸事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:37.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搜索沒有進展的情況下  就不得不確認一下有沒有漏掉線索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱衷於工作雖然是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那麼擔心黑子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:51.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼如果今晚能同床共枕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子  小小的疲勞馬上就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  姐姐大人真是個容易害羞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AIM擴散力場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對能力者來說是非常貼近身邊的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:18.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂AIM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:22.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是An Involuntary Movement「無自覺」的縮寫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:27.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是能力者在不知不覺中發散到周圍的微小的力量的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的五感是無法感覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須使用專用的器械方可檢測到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:38.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在在這個領域的研究已經在不斷地在發展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時能一起去「seventh mist」買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  風紀委員的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微晚一點沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巡邏的時候去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回不能這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是這樣的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你們每個人體內發散出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再稍微借些錢來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:22.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  前些天借給你的錢好像還沒…還吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過會全部還你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我有錢了以後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無期限  無利息  無限制不是你的賣點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛就這麼一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  在風紀委員來之前快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:49.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕鬆鬆啊  他們不是都在事後才來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  到底在幹些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼風紀委員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你們無能我才會遭受這種待遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再多有點線索就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:23.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在知道的就只有「對方是大能力以上的能力者」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:23.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是書庫找不到符合條件的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:33.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  是在短時間內突然大幅提升力量的能力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:37.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  無論如何在短時間內是不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事根本不可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從頭開始對遺留物品檢測一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟黑子一樣  初春同學也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今天也請她一起來買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  在抓到爆炸狂人之前也是沒辦法的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:31.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點  不知所以然的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:38.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春和白井同學作為風紀委員一直在努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:38.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而御阪學姐是很厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得「我完全沒什麼用啊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:51.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  抱歉  其實也沒那麼沉重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:54.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…如果我也有能力的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常生活會不會有所改變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有「幻想御手」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為超能力也就不是夢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想御手？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前談論過的都市傳說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是可以把能力的等級輕而易舉地提高的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然連脫衣女都存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想說不定真的存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能存在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:27.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟姐姐大人一起買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個那天都不用當班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:43.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就跟佐天同學說「就當讓她們放鬆一下怎麼樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:50.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  雖然很難得還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再稍微調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:56.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:00.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嶄新的世界即將來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將會拯救我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來白井同學沒有來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有拯救我的風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學有什麼想去看看的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…也沒什麼特別想去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘！像這樣的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的東西怎麼能穿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:31.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿了這個即便讓我掀了裙子也能堂堂正正地讓周圍的人看了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別讓人看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別掀起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  御阪學姐  有什麼想看的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:42.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看一下睡衣之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  是這裏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然逛過很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是沒找到一件好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:06.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來看看  這個好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春過來看一下這件睡衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:14.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣小孩子氣的款式現在已經沒有人穿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在小學生的時候還是穿著這種款式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的確有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:24.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的也是呢  都已經是中學生了怎麼可能穿這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣在那邊就有了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:34.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:37.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是睡衣  又不是讓人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學這個有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊辟里啪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為為為什麼你會在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是常盤台的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  丟了包的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？  你有妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:17.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽這孩子說想找洋裝店就給她帶路來到這裏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  是哥哥帶我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:31.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能像電視裏面的人一樣穿著洋裝的打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:36.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  像現在這副打扮也很漂亮可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟某位穿短褲的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  想打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼之前懸而未決的決鬥就在這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:48.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你的腦子裏就只有這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算在這人員密集的地方開打麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥  我想去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:05.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  大姐姐  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  出什麼事了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:20.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:33.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到那傢伙就總是控制不住情緒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  完全就不像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:13:00.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是使用了相同作案手法的不同犯人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是各起事件間都難以找到聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:10.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不抓緊的話  又會有新的受害者出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也得掌握些線索才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同事中可是有九人負了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:20.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說你不覺得太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道犯人的目標是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視衛星觀測到有重力子的活動加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  你的手機有沒有響？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:39.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:41.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  虛空爆炸事件有新情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:50.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市的監視衛星觀測到重力子出現劇烈的加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀…觀測地點在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在請求附近的警備員緊急出動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  請把觀測地點告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是第七學區的洋裝店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「seventh mist」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「seventh mist」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  我現在就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去把客人們疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:13.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜地聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:28.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經知道犯人的下一個襲擊目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這家店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你協助我進行人群的避難工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:36.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學就趕緊去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春你也要小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的目標是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位顧客請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:58.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於店內的電路系統發生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:03.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事出突然  今日的營業時間到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:06.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員會為客人指示出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼故障啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家才剛剛到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:12.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辟里啪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是和你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說還留在店裏麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:32.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有顧客都成功撤離了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在馬上離開那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在過去的事件中的人員損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有風紀委員而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人真正的目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身處觀測地點附近的風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的目標就是你啊  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:01.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:06.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個戴著眼鏡的大哥哥讓我交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:07.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃  那是炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超電磁炮把炸彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:17.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:31.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是最近的那個連續炸彈襲擊事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面好像還有人沒有撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員可真靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險  請退後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸能夠掌握更強大的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再增加點數量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:59.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是無能的風紀委員還是那群不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:59.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個不剩地全部炸飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:13.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你有什麼事就不需要我再多嘴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:18.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈狂人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:23.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我完全就聽不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  就威力來說還真是不可小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傷亡者了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連個受到擦傷的人都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我的最大輸出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從外面一眼就能看出炸彈的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才會以為裏面的人難以倖免啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超…超電磁炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(342,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:06.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到常盤台的王牌登場了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當我想做些什麼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:14.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會被力量徹底打趴在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要宰了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你這樣的人不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:24.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有力量的傢伙有哪一個不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:28.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你滿口力量  力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把牙關咬緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:42.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打了也是活該
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:58.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最不屑的  就是像你這種將力量當做擋箭牌的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:05.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盤台的超電磁炮當初也不過是個低能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:05.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:05.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(470,328)\fs18}Level 1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她通過不同尋常的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終造就了一身被稱作超能力者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:15.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  哪怕她只是一個低能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:15.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(416,328)\fs18}Level 1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:19.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人也會擋在你的面前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:50.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  多虧了御阪學姐  你看我毫髮無傷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是常盤台的大姐姐救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:58.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:03.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  竟然只有初春她們所在的地方得以倖免
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要如何使用能力才能做到這個地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可真是立了大功一件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:31.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天姐姐大人無論說什麼黑子都會照做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫您刷背也好  按摩也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼您儘管提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你的慾望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:40.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時  我的超電磁炮沒能趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(325,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:37.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正救下初春她們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:42.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:47.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中埋伏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:49.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不介意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:50.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:55.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都以為是我保護了那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:58.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報上名字的話就是「英雄」了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:01.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:05.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然大家都沒事  還在意那些幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:08.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰救的不都一樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:18.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:24.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是在耍帥罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:26.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還偏偏只對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:29.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:32.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  那傢伙總是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:33.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是氣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:36.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是面紅耳赤的時候  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:36.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰面紅耳赤了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:38.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:39.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是指夕陽

